# üåê Complete Site Architecture

## üéØ Site Overview

The **Ashish Tandon Portfolio** is designed as a comprehensive, AI-powered personal portfolio that showcases professional excellence through modern web technologies and intelligent personalization. This document details the complete site structure, section architecture, and user experience design.

